  @ctl_a    @alt_s    @met_d    @sft_f    h         @sft_j    @met_k    @alt_l    @ctl_sc
  n         m         ,         .
  @esc_imm  bspc      @s_cap    @nav
)

(deflayer symbols
  _         =         S-[       S-]       S--       S-\
  _         _         _         _         S-`       [         ]         \         grv
  -         S-=       _         _
  _         _         _         _
)

(deflayer nav-layer
  _         _         pgup      up        pgdn      _
  _         _         _         _         bspc      left      down      right     del
  home      _         end       _
  _         _         _         _
)
Changes made to fix the syntax:
| becomes S-\ (Shifted backslash)

{ becomes S-[ (Shifted left bracket)

} becomes S-] (Shifted right bracket)

~ becomes S- ` (Shifted backtick/grave)

+ becomes S-= (Shifted equals)

_ becomes S-- (Shifted minus)

This should clear the "Unknown key" error and get your symbol layer running exactly as mapped.





